                <h5>
                    <span>Anchorage is a tribute</span> to seafarers and towards their commitment towards this
                    profession.
                    Set up in 2019 after Capt Vishal suffered a near fatal stroke on board vessel amidst Singapore
                    straits leaving him with permanent damages.
                    Anchorage is a new and moder guest house with 28 rooms spread over 1 building and 1 Hotel in
                    Mahipalpur, within close proximity to the airport and well connected with metro network to all parts
                    of Delhi. The hotel and guest house is in vicinity of AIROCITY and other popular tourist spots like
                    Qutb Minar and Ambience Emporio and DLF malls. Anchorage was set up under the guidance of Capt
                    Vishal who due to his long experience with sailing understands the requirements of seafarers and
                    those of companies as well.
                    Anchorage is a humble attempt to give to seafarers at a nominal cost the excellent quality and
                    service which they deliver each tine while at work at sea with reliabilty and consistency.
                </h5>
